Cross society, who will be responsible for the disaster relief.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, the Red Cross society has called on local residents
to make donations for the flood victims. It has set up a special
account for donators.
</P>
<P>
In another development, the Chinese Education Society of Macao
has collected a total of over 280,000 Patacas (about 35,400 US
dollars) of donations from students, teachers and parents of
students during a recent collection movement. 
