The center aims to promote women's health and welfare by
ensuring a safer motherhood and reducing maternity deaths.
</P>
<P>
It also seeks to help the training of female health personnel
and development of a referral system to transfer difficult cases
to medical facilities at higher levels.
</P>
<P>
The grant will be used to procure medical equipment in addition
to financing the construction of the center.
</P>
<P>
The debt relief grant, amounting to 28.1 million rupees
(803,000 dollars), is aimed at strengthening the friendly and
cooperative relations between Japan and Pakistan, a press release
said.  
