<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, July 31 (Xinhua) -- Kenyan President Daniel arap Moi
left here early this morning for Tanznia's northern town of
Arusha to attend a one-day Heads of State regional summit on
Burundi.
</P>
<P>
Burundi's Major Pierre Buyoya toppled President Sylvestre
Ntibantunganya in a military coup last Thursday. The coup has
been widely condemned by leaders in the region and the
